Test Release Blog Locally
===========

On Ubuntu/Debian:
$ git clone the repo
$ apt-get install jekyll
$ jekyll serve
$ Go to http://localhost:4000

On OSX:
$ git clone the repo
$ gem install github-pages
$ cd release-blog 
$ jekyll serve
$ Go to http://localhost:4000


Flags
===========

$ --no-watch  (Do not watch for changes)
$ --watch (Make changes on the fly)
$ --trace (For debug)



